&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Can structure a complete narrative and be able to write in different voices to suit client and audience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with ACD, Copy to produce standout and strategically focused campaigns and experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and interview prospective creative candidates&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage teams, creative output and client relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Concepts, campaign execution that are in line with client strategy&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee day to day deliverables for team under tight deadlines while delivering best in class work to market.&lt;/li&gt;
