&lt;p&gt;Discover your purpose. Embrace innovation. Experience #LifeatRealChem.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;21GRAMS, part of Real Chemistry, takes an innovative approach to advertising, and focusing on making healthcare more human.&amp;nbsp; Not just in our work, but in the way we conduct business, approach client relationships, and treat each other. It’s a place where people subscribe to the adage, “Be good to each other, but hard on the work.” A place where people are not just in it for the paycheck, but to make a dent in the universe. Sound like you?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are currently seeking a savvy &lt;strong&gt;Copy Supervisor &lt;/strong&gt;to join our growing &lt;strong&gt;Market Access Team!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for a strategic healthcare writer who excels at translating complex clinical, economic, and outcomes data into compelling narratives that resonate with payer, provider, health system, and access stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Copy Supervisor serves as the lead writer on assigned brands and market access initiatives, partnering closely with strategy, creative, medical, account, and client teams to develop impactful communications that support product value and access goals. The ideal candidate combines exceptional writing skills with a strong understanding of market access, reimbursement, HEOR, and value communication principles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to developing high-quality content, the Copy Supervisor will mentor junior writers, contribute to team growth, and help elevate the quality and strategic rigor of agency deliverables.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
